# Azure MCP Server

Use the Azure MCP Server (@azure/mcp) to interact with Azure services via natural language. Version: 2.0.0-beta.28.

## Quick Start

Before using Azure MCP tools, ensure you're authenticated:
```bash
az login
az account show  # verify subscription
```

## Server Modes

Configure the mode based on your needs:

| Mode | Tools | Best For |
|------|-------|----------|
| `namespace` (default) | ~40 (one per service) | General use |
| `consolidated` | Curated groups | AI agents (recommended) |
| `all` | 200+ individual | Granular control |

```json
{
  "args": ["-y", "@azure/mcp@2.0.0-beta.28", "server", "start", "--mode", "consolidated"]
}
```

